Definition: the superlative of `little' that can be used with mass nouns and is usually preceded by `the'
Example: a quantifier meaning smallest in amount or extent or degree; didn't care the least bit; he has the least talent of anyone
Synonyms: a, MOST, noun, communication, superlative, u, the, of, little, that, can, be, used, with, mass, nouns, and, is, usually, preceded, by, quantifier, meaning, smallest, in, amount, or, extent, degree, didn, t, care, least, bit, he, has, talent, anyone
Category: adj.all
